measurements.description:
Three hundred twenty-two flowers and six buds on 23 up-to 15-cm inflorescences;
	well displayed around a cleanly grown 38-cm wide x 23-cm tall plant grown in bark in a 10-cm plastic pot;

	sepals and petals cream white overlaid pink, blotched dark rose;
	lip saccate, yellow, rose band at midpoint; anther cap white;

	substance avearage; texture diamond dust; commended for excellent culture in a small pot.
